title: Govinda's Gourmet
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Indian, Asian, Vedic
description: Govinda's To-Go Cafe is a vegan friendly, sit-down dining place. Features a nearly all vegan menu (2 non-vegan dishes) with Asian and American regional influences and a vegan Indian food buffet. Confirmed open Feb. 2014, just enter through the to-go side due to construction. Confirmed open, July 2014.
